OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsunny into the evening, with clear
OL,7,Fspells overnight, cloud increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west towards dawn. Much
OL,9,Fcooler than recent nights. Mostly
OL,10,Flight southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA sunny start to the day, but
OL,13,Fskies turning hazy, leading to bright
OL,14,Fspells during the afternoon.
OL,15,FTemperatures close to the late June
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
